852
00:34:50,040 --> 00:34:52,320
Kamusta ang bago mong kwarto?

853
00:34:53,150 --> 00:34:55,210
Ilang araw na lang. Kaya kong gawin.

854
00:34:57,070 --> 00:34:58,110
Kapag natapos na ang kaganapan,

855
00:34:58,110 --> 00:34:58,970
