893
00:36:54,800 --> 00:36:56,260
Bakit isa na lang ang natitira?

894
00:36:59,030 --> 00:37:00,840
May kinuha ba akong pagkain?

895
00:37:00,860 --> 00:37:02,900
Ano ang pinagsasabi mo?

896
00:37:03,230 --> 00:37:04,280
Ikaw ang aming pinuno.

897
00:37:04,280 --> 00:37:06,340
Syempre may box lunch para sayo.

898
00:37:07,030 --> 00:37:08,230
Paumanhin, Ms. Xu.

899
00:37:08,400 --> 00:37:09,710
Hindi sapat ang box lunch namin.

900
00:37:09,710 --> 00:37:12,370
Pumunta sa cafeteria
at tingnan kung may natitira pa.

901
00:37:14,110 --> 00:37:15,210
Sobrang sama ng pakiramdam ko.

902
00:37:15,400 --> 00:37:17,330
Paano kung mag-order ako sa iyo ng takeout?

903
00:37:17,400 --> 00:37:18,190
Hindi na kailangan.

904
00:37:19,070 --> 00:37:19,930
Hindi ako nagugutom.

905
00:37:22,030 --> 00:37:24,110
Ms. Xu, maaari mong makuha ang akin.

906
00:37:24,110 --> 00:37:25,440
Naging abala ka buong araw.

907
00:37:25,440 --> 00:37:26,840
ayos lang. kainin mo.

908
00:37:30,710 --> 00:37:31,710
Bilisan mo kumain.

909
00:37:34,920 --> 00:37:35,880
Kumain pa.

910
00:37:41,510 --> 00:37:42,320
Mr. Ji.

911
00:37:44,320 --> 00:37:45,510
Hindi ka pa naghahapunan diba?

912
00:37:45,510 --> 00:37:46,070
Dito.

913
00:37:48,190 --> 00:37:49,070
